init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The film that you are watching is your next life, and you can enter into your own body when the movie starts.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Then you leave, and watch the rest of your life on the screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When you are in 7th grade, and just starting puberty, you visit yourself again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You try to help yourself out with a little advice, but you see that your college self is getting involved in some bad things.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You watch, horrified, as your future self drops out of college and starts a downward spiral.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Why are you trying to sabotage my efforts?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He moves in close and places his hand on your knee.
